@NODE INTRO "What is Learn A Language?"

Learn A Language is a language program... In the following the features are
listet.

 - The internal translate-program can translate whole files.

 - The lexicon allows pattern-input and list-print of the words.

 - At a asking there will be by request only the words questioned, which
   at the last asking not were known.

 - Forms can be asked, too.

 - A special type-asking is possible.

 - You can adjust the number of the words to ask, degree of difficulty
   and many more.

 - The result of a asking can be saved, printed out and viewed in a
   graphical representation.

 - The words-editor has many edit-commands and allows a fast input.

 - For every word you can define several variants, forms and a type.
 
 - The program-language can be switched (German/English).


The original release of Learn A Language includes the following things:

 - The latest original release

 - A german-english word file (over than 2000 words, standard vocabulary,
   forms of the irregular verbs (Past Tense, Past Participle), type:
   substantives, adjectives, verbs)

 - A german-latin word file (ca. 2000 words, forms of the verbs,
   substantives with genitive, type: substantives, adjectives, verbs)

 - Several programs for Learn A Language

 - Update-service

 - Hotline for questions or problems
@ENDNODE

